{% comment %}
  Main Product — Milestones 1-5 (unchanged, see prior inline comments)
  + final pass: Inventory & Availability, Product Information accordions,
  Related Products.

  Inventory: low-stock threshold is a hardcoded 5 (inventory_quantity <=
  5), not a merchant setting — deliberate simplification, can become
  configurable later if needed. Availability state (in stock / low stock
  / backorder / sold out) mirrors the same instant-update discipline as
  price/image from Milestone 3: the variants JSON payload also carries
  inventory_tracked/inventory_quantity/continue_selling, and
  VariantPicker recomputes the same 4-state logic client-side so
  switching variants without a reload keeps quantity's max and the
  status text in sync — leaving them stale after a JS-driven switch
  would be a real regression given Milestone 3 already made everything
  else instant.

  Accordions: native disclosure elements (details/summary) — free
  keyboard support, no
  ARIA needed, no JS. Product description itself is left exactly as
  Milestone 1 built it (plain, always visible) rather than folded into
  an accordion, since moving already-working content would cross into
  "refactoring existing code"; only Shipping/Returns/Care Instructions
  are new accordion panels, sourced from new richtext settings (this
  section's first-ever schema settings array). Each is independently
  optional and simply doesn't render if left blank.

  Related Products: real Shopify recommendations (routes.
  product_recommendations_url, fetched via product-form.js), with a
  same-collection server-rendered fallback that is what actually shows
  on a normal page load (recommendations.performed is only ever true
  when Shopify's recommendations-rendering context fetches this exact
  markup) — so something always shows without depending on JS, and JS
  only upgrades it to genuinely algorithmic results when the fetch
  succeeds. Card markup/classes here are new and self-contained
  (main-product__recommendation-*), not the featured-collection.css
  .product-card classes — that stylesheet isn't loaded on this
  template, so reusing its class names without its CSS would silently
  produce unstyled markup. Values (aspect ratio, badge treatment,
  stretched-link pattern, typography tokens) deliberately mirror
  featured-collection.css's .product-card as closely as possible.

  No-JS baseline: all product images render as a single stacked list of
  real, individually-anchorable list items (each with its own id), with
  real anchor-linked thumbnails — native anchor-scroll, no JS. With
  JS, ProductGallery (product-form.js) adds one modifier class that
  switches the stack into "only show the active item" mode and
  intercepts thumbnail clicks to swap the active item instead of
  scrolling.

  Which image is "active" (both server-rendered and as JS's starting
  point) is computed from the CURRENT variant's featured_image, not
  simply the first image — this is what makes ?variant= deep links,
  refresh, and back/forward navigation correct without JS: since variant
  already resolves via product.selected_or_first_available_variant
  (itself already URL-?variant=-aware), the right image is correct in
  the server-rendered HTML on every fresh request, with no dependency on
  client-side state or script execution order. JS's own initial render()
  call (Milestone 3) just reconfirms the same state Liquid already set.

  Variant image integration reuses VariantPicker's existing data flow
  (Milestone 3) rather than a parallel mechanism: the JSON payload now
  carries featured_media_id (just an id) instead of a duplicated image
  URL, since the gallery already renders every image — updateImage()
  calls gallery.activateByMediaId() instead of swapping a lone <img>.
{% endcomment %}

{{ 'main-product.css' | asset_url | stylesheet_tag }}
<script src="{{ 'product-form.js' | asset_url }}" defer></script>

{%- liquid
  assign featured_image = product.featured_image
  assign variant = product.selected_or_first_available_variant
  assign compare_at_price = variant.compare_at_price
  assign price = variant.price
  assign has_variants = product.has_only_default_variant == false
  assign options = product.options_with_values
  assign option_count = options.size
  assign last_option = options.last
  assign active_media_id = variant.featured_image.id | default: product.featured_image.id
  assign low_stock_threshold = 5
  assign inventory_tracked = false
  if variant.inventory_management != blank
    assign inventory_tracked = true
  endif
  assign continue_selling = false
  if variant.inventory_policy == 'continue'
    assign continue_selling = true
  endif
-%}

<section class="main-product">
  <div class="container">
    <variant-picker>
      {%- if has_variants -%}
        {%- capture variants_json -%}
          [
            {%- for v in product.variants -%}
              {
                "id": {{ v.id | json }},
                "available": {{ v.available | json }},
                "options": {{ v.options | json }},
                "price": {{ v.price | money | json }},
                "compare_at_price": {% if v.compare_at_price > v.price %}{{ v.compare_at_price | money | json }}{% else %}null{% endif %},
                "featured_media_id": {% if v.featured_image %}{{ v.featured_image.id | json }}{% else %}null{% endif %},
                "inventory_tracked": {% if v.inventory_management != blank %}true{% else %}false{% endif %},
                "inventory_quantity": {{ v.inventory_quantity | json }},
                "continue_selling": {% if v.inventory_policy == 'continue' %}true{% else %}false{% endif %}
              }{% unless forloop.last %},{% endunless %}
            {%- endfor -%}
          ]
        {%- endcapture -%}
        <script type="application/json" data-product-variants>{{ variants_json }}</script>
      {%- endif -%}

      <div class="grid md:grid--two main-product__grid">
        <div class="main-product__media">
        {%- if product.images.size > 0 -%}
          <product-gallery class="main-product__gallery" data-default-media-id="{{ product.featured_image.id }}">
            <ul class="main-product__gallery-list" role="list">
              {%- for image in product.images -%}
                {%- liquid
                  assign is_active_image = false
                  if image.id == active_media_id
                    assign is_active_image = true
                  endif
                  assign loading_attr = 'lazy'
                  assign fetchpriority_attr = 'auto'
                  if is_active_image
                    assign loading_attr = 'eager'
                    assign fetchpriority_attr = 'high'
                  endif
                -%}
                <li
                  id="Media-{{ section.id }}-{{ image.id }}"
                  class="main-product__gallery-item{% if is_active_image %} is-active{% endif %}"
                  data-media-id="{{ image.id }}"
                >
                  {{
                    image
                    | image_url: width: 1600
                    | image_tag:
                      loading: loading_attr,
                      fetchpriority: fetchpriority_attr,
                      sizes: '(min-width: 48em) 50vw, 100vw',
                      widths: '400,700,1000,1600',
                      class: 'main-product__gallery-image',
                      alt: image.alt | default: product.title | escape
                  }}
                </li>
              {%- endfor -%}
            </ul>

            {%- if product.images.size > 1 -%}
              <ul class="main-product__thumbnails" role="list">
                {%- for image in product.images -%}
                  {%- assign is_active_image = false -%}
                  {%- if image.id == active_media_id -%}
                    {%- assign is_active_image = true -%}
                  {%- endif -%}
                  <li>
                    <a
                      href="#Media-{{ section.id }}-{{ image.id }}"
                      class="main-product__thumbnail{% if is_active_image %} is-active{% endif %}"
                      data-media-id="{{ image.id }}"
                      aria-current="{{ is_active_image }}"
                    >
                      <span class="visually-hidden">{{ image.alt | default: product.title | escape }}</span>
                      {{
                        image
                        | image_url: width: 160
                        | image_tag:
                          loading: 'lazy',
                          width: 80,
                          height: 80,
                          class: 'main-product__thumbnail-image',
                          alt: ''
                      }}
                    </a>
                  </li>
                {%- endfor -%}
              </ul>
            {%- endif -%}
          </product-gallery>
        {%- else -%}
          <div class="main-product__placeholder" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 120 120" class="main-product__placeholder-mark">
              <circle cx="60" cy="60" r="38" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1"/>
              <path d="M60 40v40M40 60h40" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
        {%- endif -%}
      </div>

      <div class="main-product__content">
        {%- if product.vendor != blank -%}
          <p class="main-product__vendor">{{ product.vendor | escape }}</p>
        {%- endif -%}

        <h1 class="main-product__title">{{ product.title | escape }}</h1>

        <p class="main-product__price" aria-live="polite">
          {%- if compare_at_price > price -%}
            <span class="main-product__price--sale">{{ price | money }}</span>
            <span class="main-product__compare-price">{{ compare_at_price | money }}</span>
          {%- else -%}
            {{ price | money }}
          {%- endif -%}
        </p>

        <p
          class="main-product__availability"
          aria-live="polite"
          data-in-stock-label="{{ 'sections.main_product.in_stock' | t }}"
          data-sold-out-label="{{ 'sections.main_product.sold_out' | t }}"
          data-backorder-label="{{ 'sections.main_product.backorder' | t }}"
          data-low-stock-template="{{ 'sections.main_product.low_stock_count' | t: count: 'COUNT_PLACEHOLDER' }}"
          data-low-stock-threshold="{{ low_stock_threshold }}"
        >
          {%- if variant.available == false -%}
            <span class="main-product__availability-status main-product__availability-status--sold-out">{{ 'sections.main_product.sold_out' | t }}</span>
          {%- elsif inventory_tracked == false -%}
            <span class="main-product__availability-status main-product__availability-status--in-stock">{{ 'sections.main_product.in_stock' | t }}</span>
          {%- elsif variant.inventory_quantity <= 0 and continue_selling -%}
            <span class="main-product__availability-status main-product__availability-status--backorder">{{ 'sections.main_product.backorder' | t }}</span>
          {%- elsif variant.inventory_quantity > 0 and variant.inventory_quantity <= low_stock_threshold -%}
            <span class="main-product__availability-status main-product__availability-status--low-stock">{{ 'sections.main_product.low_stock_count' | t: count: variant.inventory_quantity }}</span>
          {%- else -%}
            <span class="main-product__availability-status main-product__availability-status--in-stock">{{ 'sections.main_product.in_stock' | t }}</span>
          {%- endif -%}
        </p>

        {%- if product.description != blank -%}
          <div class="main-product__description">{{ product.description }}</div>
        {%- endif -%}

        {%- if has_variants and option_count > 1 -%}
          <div class="main-product__options">
            {%- for option in options -%}
              {%- assign option_position = forloop.index -%}
              {%- unless forloop.last -%}
                <form method="get" action="{{ product.url }}" class="main-product__option-form">
                  <fieldset class="main-product__option">
                    <legend class="main-product__option-legend">{{ option.name | escape }}</legend>
                    <div class="main-product__option-values">
                      {%- for value in option.values -%}
                        {%- liquid
                          assign candidates = product.variants
                          for other in options
                            assign other_position = forloop.index
                            assign other_key = 'option' | append: other_position
                            if other_position == option_position
                              assign candidates = candidates | where: other_key, value
                            else
                              assign fixed_value = variant.options[forloop.index0]
                              assign candidates = candidates | where: other_key, fixed_value
                            endif
                          endfor
                          assign matched_variant = candidates.first
                          assign current_value = variant.options[option_position | minus: 1]
                          assign is_checked = false
                          if current_value == value
                            assign is_checked = true
                          endif
                          assign is_unavailable = true
                          if matched_variant != blank and matched_variant.available
                            assign is_unavailable = false
                          endif
                        -%}
                        <span class="main-product__option-value">
                          <input
                            type="radio"
                            name="variant"
                            id="Option-{{ section.id }}-{{ option_position }}-{{ forloop.index }}"
                            value="{{ matched_variant.id }}"
                            data-option-position="{{ option_position }}"
                            data-option-value="{{ value | escape }}"
                            class="main-product__option-input visually-hidden"
                            {% if is_checked %}checked{% endif %}
                            {% if is_unavailable %}disabled{% endif %}
                          >
                          <label for="Option-{{ section.id }}-{{ option_position }}-{{ forloop.index }}" class="main-product__option-label">
                            {{ value | escape }}
                            {%- if is_unavailable -%}
                              <span class="visually-hidden"> ({{ 'sections.main_product.sold_out' | t }})</span>
                            {%- endif -%}
                          </label>
                        </span>
                      {%- endfor -%}
                    </div>
                  </fieldset>
                  <button type="submit" class="main-product__option-update">
                    {{ 'sections.main_product.update_selection' | t }}
                  </button>
                </form>
              {%- endunless -%}
            {%- endfor -%}
          </div>
        {%- endif -%}

        {%- form 'product', product, class: 'main-product__form' -%}
          {%- if has_variants -%}
            {%- assign last_option_position = option_count -%}
            <fieldset class="main-product__option">
              <legend class="main-product__option-legend">{{ last_option.name | escape }}</legend>
              <div class="main-product__option-values">
                {%- for value in last_option.values -%}
                  {%- liquid
                    assign candidates = product.variants
                    for other in options
                      assign other_position = forloop.index
                      assign other_key = 'option' | append: other_position
                      if other_position == last_option_position
                        assign candidates = candidates | where: other_key, value
                      else
                        assign fixed_value = variant.options[forloop.index0]
                        assign candidates = candidates | where: other_key, fixed_value
                      endif
                    endfor
                    assign matched_variant = candidates.first
                    assign current_value = variant.options[last_option_position | minus: 1]
                    assign is_checked = false
                    if current_value == value
                      assign is_checked = true
                    endif
                    assign is_unavailable = true
                    if matched_variant != blank and matched_variant.available
                      assign is_unavailable = false
                    endif
                  -%}
                  <span class="main-product__option-value">
                    <input
                      type="radio"
                      name="id"
                      id="Option-{{ section.id }}-final-{{ forloop.index }}"
                      value="{{ matched_variant.id }}"
                      data-option-position="{{ last_option_position }}"
                      data-option-value="{{ value | escape }}"
                      class="main-product__option-input visually-hidden"
                      {% if is_checked %}checked{% endif %}
                      {% if is_unavailable %}disabled{% endif %}
                    >
                    <label for="Option-{{ section.id }}-final-{{ forloop.index }}" class="main-product__option-label">
                      {{ value | escape }}
                      {%- if is_unavailable -%}
                        <span class="visually-hidden"> ({{ 'sections.main_product.sold_out' | t }})</span>
                      {%- endif -%}
                    </label>
                  </span>
                {%- endfor -%}
              </div>
            </fieldset>
          {%- else -%}
            <input type="hidden" name="id" value="{{ variant.id }}">
          {%- endif -%}

          <quantity-selector class="main-product__quantity">
            <label for="Quantity-{{ section.id }}" class="main-product__quantity-label">
              {{ 'sections.main_product.quantity_label' | t }}
            </label>
            <div class="main-product__quantity-controls">
              <button
                type="button"
                class="main-product__quantity-button main-product__quantity-button--decrease"
                aria-label="{{ 'sections.main_product.decrease_quantity' | t }}"
                aria-controls="Quantity-{{ section.id }}"
              >&minus;</button>
              <input
                type="number"
                name="quantity"
                id="Quantity-{{ section.id }}"
                class="main-product__quantity-input"
                value="1"
                min="1"
                {% if inventory_tracked and continue_selling == false and variant.inventory_quantity > 0 %}
                  max="{{ variant.inventory_quantity }}"
                {% endif %}
                inputmode="numeric"
              >
              <button
                type="button"
                class="main-product__quantity-button main-product__quantity-button--increase"
                aria-label="{{ 'sections.main_product.increase_quantity' | t }}"
                aria-controls="Quantity-{{ section.id }}"
              >&plus;</button>
            </div>
          </quantity-selector>

          <button
            type="submit"
            name="add"
            class="main-product__button"
            data-add-to-cart-label="{{ 'sections.main_product.add_to_cart' | t }}"
            data-sold-out-label="{{ 'sections.main_product.sold_out' | t }}"
            {% if variant.available == false %}disabled{% endif %}
          >
            {%- if variant.available -%}
              {{ 'sections.main_product.add_to_cart' | t }}
            {%- else -%}
              {{ 'sections.main_product.sold_out' | t }}
            {%- endif -%}
          </button>

          <div class="main-product__dynamic-checkout">
            {{ form | payment_button }}
          </div>
        {%- endform -%}

        {%- if section.settings.shipping_content != blank or section.settings.returns_content != blank or section.settings.care_content != blank -%}
          <div class="main-product__accordions">
            {%- if section.settings.shipping_content != blank -%}
              <details class="main-product__accordion">
                <summary class="main-product__accordion-summary">{{ 'sections.main_product.shipping_heading' | t }}</summary>
                <div class="main-product__accordion-content">{{ section.settings.shipping_content }}</div>
              </details>
            {%- endif -%}
            {%- if section.settings.returns_content != blank -%}
              <details class="main-product__accordion">
                <summary class="main-product__accordion-summary">{{ 'sections.main_product.returns_heading' | t }}</summary>
                <div class="main-product__accordion-content">{{ section.settings.returns_content }}</div>
              </details>
            {%- endif -%}
            {%- if section.settings.care_content != blank -%}
              <details class="main-product__accordion">
                <summary class="main-product__accordion-summary">{{ 'sections.main_product.care_heading' | t }}</summary>
                <div class="main-product__accordion-content">{{ section.settings.care_content }}</div>
              </details>
            {%- endif -%}
          </div>
        {%- endif -%}
      </div>
      </div>
    </variant-picker>
  </div>
</section>

{%- liquid
  assign show_recommendations = recommendations.performed
  assign display_products = recommendations.products
  if show_recommendations == false
    assign fallback_collection = product.collections.first
    assign display_products = fallback_collection.products
  endif
-%}

<product-recommendations
  id="ProductRecommendations-{{ section.id }}"
  class="main-product__recommendations"
  data-url="{{ routes.product_recommendations_url }}?section_id={{ section.id }}&product_id={{ product.id }}&limit=4&intent=related"
>
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="main-product__recommendations-heading">{{ 'sections.main_product.related_heading' | t }}</h2>

    {%- assign shown_count = 0 -%}
    <ul class="grid md:grid--two main-product__recommendations-grid" role="list">
      {%- for item in display_products -%}
        {%- unless item.id == product.id -%}
          {%- if shown_count < 4 -%}
            {%- assign shown_count = shown_count | plus: 1 -%}
            <li>
              <div class="main-product__recommendation-card">
                <div class="main-product__recommendation-media">
                  {%- if item.featured_image != blank -%}
                    {{
                      item.featured_image
                      | image_url: width: 800
                      | image_tag:
                        loading: 'lazy',
                        sizes: '(min-width: 48em) 25vw, 50vw',
                        widths: '300,500,800',
                        class: 'main-product__recommendation-image',
                        alt: item.featured_image.alt | default: item.title | escape
                    }}
                  {%- else -%}
                    <div class="main-product__recommendation-placeholder" aria-hidden="true">
                      <svg viewBox="0 0 120 120" class="main-product__recommendation-placeholder-mark">
                        <circle cx="60" cy="60" r="38" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1"/>
                        <path d="M60 40v40M40 60h40" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1"/>
                      </svg>
                    </div>
                  {%- endif -%}

                  {%- if item.available == false -%}
                    <span class="main-product__recommendation-badge main-product__recommendation-badge--sold-out">{{ 'sections.main_product.sold_out' | t }}</span>
                  {%- elsif item.compare_at_price > item.price -%}
                    <span class="main-product__recommendation-badge main-product__recommendation-badge--sale">{{ 'sections.main_product.sale_badge' | t }}</span>
                  {%- endif -%}
                </div>

                <div class="main-product__recommendation-content">
                  <h3 class="main-product__recommendation-title">
                    <a href="{{ item.url }}" class="main-product__recommendation-link">{{ item.title | escape }}</a>
                  </h3>
                  <p class="main-product__recommendation-price">
                    {%- if item.compare_at_price > item.price -%}
                      <span class="main-product__recommendation-price--sale">{{ item.price | money }}</span>
                      <span class="main-product__recommendation-compare-price">{{ item.compare_at_price | money }}</span>
                    {%- else -%}
                      {{ item.price | money }}
                    {%- endif -%}
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </li>
          {%- endif -%}
        {%- endunless -%}
      {%- endfor -%}
    </ul>

    {%- if shown_count == 0 -%}
      <p class="main-product__recommendations-empty">{{ 'sections.main_product.related_empty' | t }}</p>
    {%- endif -%}
  </div>
</product-recommendations>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "Product information",
  "settings": [
    {
      "type": "header",
      "content": "Product information"
    },
    {
      "type": "richtext",
      "id": "shipping_content",
      "label": "Shipping content",
      "info": "Optional. Leave blank to hide this section."
    },
    {
      "type": "richtext",
      "id": "returns_content",
      "label": "Returns content",
      "info": "Optional. Leave blank to hide this section."
    },
    {
      "type": "richtext",
      "id": "care_content",
      "label": "Care instructions",
      "info": "Optional. Leave blank to hide this section."
    }
  ]
}
{% endschema %}
